value.author: Mark Hazleton

value.message:
Update inherits attributes and enhance documentation

Updated the `inherits` attribute in various ASP.NET Web Forms pages and user controls from `App_Web_c1xchfhz` to `App_Web_chn4v2ow` to reflect changes in dynamically generated class names. This update affects multiple files, including `Chart.aspx`, `DataTable.aspx`, `Default.aspx`, and others.

Added a new section titled "Copilot Instructions for Data Analytics Demo (DAWPM)" to the `copilot-instructions.md` file, providing an overview of the project, architecture, key technologies, and detailed instructions for building and deploying the application.
value.author: Mark Hazleton

value.author: Mark Hazleton

value.message:
feat: Add custom styles and functionality for Pivot Table implementation

- Introduced pivot.css for custom styling of pivot table components.
- Implemented app.js to initialize the Data Analysis Demo application with global event handlers and utility functions.
- Added datatables.js for DataTables configuration and utility functions.
- Created pivot.js for enhanced PivotTable utilities with error handling and performance monitoring.
- Updated site.js to serve as a single entry point for all client-side dependencies and initialize components.
- Included vendor.js for core vendor libraries and Bootstrap component initialization.
- Configured webpack to bundle JavaScript and CSS files, optimizing for production.
value.author: Mark Hazleton

value.message:
Update .gitignore to include .vscode directory

Added the .vscode directory to the .gitignore file to prevent local development environment settings from being tracked in the repository. This ensures that only relevant project files are included in version control.
